---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';

const title = 'fun clicker | Privacy Policy';
const lastUpdated = '2026-02-13';
---

<SiteLayout
  title={title}
  description="How FunClicker.click collects, uses, and protects information, including advertising and cookies."
  canonicalPath="/privacy-policy"
>
  <section class="space-y-8 border-none">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase italic">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm font-medium leading-loose text-gray-700">
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how FunClicker.click ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and shares
        information when you visit our website (the "Service").
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>
          <strong>Information you provide:</strong> if you contact us, we may receive your name, email address, and the
          content of your message.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Automatically collected information:</strong> IP-derived region, browser/device type, pages viewed,
          referral source, and interaction events.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>
      <p>
        We may use cookies, local storage, and similar technologies to operate the site, analyze usage, prevent abuse,
        and support advertising. You can control cookies through your browser settings.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Advertising (Google AdSense)</h2>
      <p>
        We use third-party advertising services such as Google AdSense. Google and its partners may use cookies to
        serve and measure ads based on your visits to this or other websites.
      </p>
      <p>
        Learn how Google uses information from sites or apps that use Google services:
        <a
          class="underline font-black text-black"
          href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          target="_blank"
        >
          policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites
        </a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Analytics and Diagnostics</h2>
      <p>
        We may use analytics tools (including Microsoft Clarity) to understand site performance and user experience.
        These tools may collect usage and device data through cookies or similar identifiers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">How We Use Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>To provide and maintain the Service.</li>
        <li>To respond to user inquiries and legal notices.</li>
        <li>To improve performance, usability, and content quality.</li>
        <li>To detect abuse, fraud, security incidents, or technical failures.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Sharing of Information</h2>
      <p>
        We may share limited information with service providers that help us run the site, such as hosting, analytics,
        and advertising partners. We may also disclose information when required by law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Children&apos;s Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This Service is not directed to children under 13. If you believe a child has provided personal information,
        contact us and we will review and remove it where appropriate.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Your Choices</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Manage cookies in your browser settings.</li>
        <li>Use Google ad settings and opt-out controls where available.</li>
        <li>Contact us to request deletion of messages sent to our support email.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-black uppercase text-black">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact
        <a class="underline font-black text-black" href="mailto:contact@funclicker.click">contact@funclicker.click</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
